{"tid":2357532,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"傳真社：龍門老闆曾稱賣股份割蓆  公司註冊顯示仍與富臨關連人士持有公司","createTime":"2021-01-07T13:07:16.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-07T14:49:23.000Z","uid":4646,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"d144adf58dd6e0016a42ca23f373dacf7ee09eb7","tid":2357532,"uid":4646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T13:07:16.000Z","msg":"【龍門爭議】香港政治環境催生了「黃藍經濟圈」，意指透過光顧政見相近的商家令該陣營壯大，但亦出現一些爭議。傳真社過去半年收到近10宗投訴，指「黃店」龍門冰室處理「捐款」用途與聲稱不符，包括去年初開展16個項目收入高達2,300多萬元，但最後倒蝕過百萬元，質疑負責人張俊傑處理帳目有問題，希望傳真社介入調查。基於公眾利益，記者嘗試比對各項帳目及張俊傑對外聲稱是否屬實，並將資料整理公開，由大眾自行判斷。<br />\n投訴另一主要內容是質疑龍門與「藍店」富臨有利益關係，張俊傑曾為雙方早年的合作解畫，稱2019年9月已「不收分文」出售與富臨有關的龍門股份，損失60萬元。富臨亦回應本社時指集團與龍門並無關聯。不過公司註冊處最新年報紀錄顯示，張俊傑仍與一名富臨關連人士共同持有一間公司，該公司曾為龍門冰室簽訂租約。<br />\n傳真社透過電話、Whatsapp、Facebook、電郵及到冰室接觸張俊傑，向他提供相關資料希望他回應以釋除公眾疑慮，他均拒絕接受訪問及提供資料。<br />\n足本報道：<br />\n龍門老闆曾稱賣股份割蓆  公司註冊顯示仍與富臨關連人士持有公司<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/3bnBaql\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F3bnBaql&d=vTNdr7lgiRBdtcQZ4wg6z9g1hcd%2FKl8HgBLPnoE2n08%3D&h=642327f1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/3bnBaql</a><br />\n龍門開16項目籌基金收入2千多萬  最終倒蝕百萬被質疑賬目不清<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2XkZFfi\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2XkZFfi&d=vTNdr7lgiRBdtcQZ4wg6z9g1hcd%2FKl8HgBLPnoE2n08%3D&h=01acdabe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2XkZFfi</a><br />\n英文版本：<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2Xgx2jB\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2Xgx2jB&d=vTNdr7lgiRBdtcQZ4wg6z9g1hcd%2FKl8HgBLPnoE2n08%3D&h=97a800b6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2Xgx2jB</a><br />\n加入訂閱，撐起真相：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.factwire.org/backus/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.factwire.org%2Fbackus%2F&d=vTNdr7lgiRBdtcQZ4wg6z9g1hcd%2FKl8HgBLPnoE2n08%3D&h=df365111\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.factwire.org/backus/</a><br />\n報料：Whatsapp/Telegram 9639 7479<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg3-2.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/135181601_1646186292255085_6766260194816264359_o.jpg?_nc_cat=101&amp;ccb=2&amp;_nc_sid=730e14&amp;_nc_ohc=3Ltr7Lo2bSkAX9NFOH6&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg3-2.fna&amp;oh=dc0a8d799a96d382388199d450efe897&amp;oe=601E11BA\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg3-2.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F135181601_1646186292255085_6766260194816264359_o.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D101%26ccb%3D2%26_nc_sid%3D730e14%26_nc_ohc%3D3Ltr7Lo2bSkAX9NFOH6%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg3-2.fna%26oh%3Ddc0a8d799a96d382388199d450efe897%26oe%3D601E11BA&h=957cabc8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"706b60f465a1aeec433550a8f5e85fa8cfbba7b7","tid":2357532,"uid":4646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T13:07:43.000Z","msg":"龍門與富臨的公司股權關係：<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg3-2.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/134942158_1646189835588064_6107381186465024510_o.png?_nc_cat=102&amp;ccb=2&amp;_nc_sid=dbeb18&amp;_nc_ohc=FB1SUBeGlagAX_EWquo&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg3-2.fna&amp;oh=c2a0c9fd3bf55c60ae53c3470a0c0bf0&amp;oe=601D494C\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg3-2.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F134942158_1646189835588064_6107381186465024510_o.png%3F_nc_cat%3D102%26ccb%3D2%26_nc_sid%3Ddbeb18%26_nc_ohc%3DFB1SUBeGlagAX_EWquo%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg3-2.fna%26oh%3Dc2a0c9fd3bf55c60ae53c3470a0c0bf0%26oe%3D601D494C&h=35467abd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d038c1fabd12a44c456690129f1bc6762d73fa91","tid":2357532,"uid":4646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T13:07:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/factwire/photos/p.1646189832254731/1646189832254731?type=3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Ffactwire%2Fphotos%2Fp.1646189832254731%2F1646189832254731%3Ftype%3D3&d=vTNdr7lgiRBdtcQZ4wg6z9g1hcd%2FKl8HgBLPnoE2n08%3D&h=08f97e03\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/factwire/photos/p.1646189832254731/1646189832254731?type=3<